'''梅·蕙絲''' ({{lang-en|Mae West}}，{{bd|1893年|8月7日|1980年|11月22日}}<ref>{{cite book|last=Yeatts|first=Tabatha |title=The Legendary Mae West|publisher=2000|date=Lulu.com|pages=5|isbn=0-967-91581-3|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Cullen|first=Frank |coauthors=Hackman, Florence; McNeilly, Donald|title=Vaudeville, Old & New: An Encyclopedia of Variety Performers in America|url=https://archive.org/details/vaudevilleoldnew00cull|publisher=Routledge|date=2007|pages=[https://archive.org/details/vaudevilleoldnew00cull/page/1183 1183]|isbn=0-415-93853-8|language=en}}</ref>)，[[演員|演員]]、[[劇作家|劇作家]]、螢幕[[編劇|編劇]]、也是美國眾所週知的[[性感偶像|性感偶像]]。

梅·蕙絲最為人所熟知的是其黃色的[[雙關語|雙關語]]，在到好萊塢為電影產業寫劇本、做諧星、演員之前，她就在紐約的劇場舞台上以[[綜藝表演|綜藝表演]](Vaudeville)而小有名氣。她是演藝生涯中遭遇最多爭議的女星，蕙絲面對許多問題，包含審查制度。

在她結束銀幕生涯後，仍繼續在舞台上演出，在[[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]、英國、廣播或者電視，並錄製了她的[[搖滾|搖滾]]專輯。

==生平==
蕙絲原來在紐約布魯克林區布什威克出生時名字為'''瑪麗·珍·蕙絲''' ('''Mary Jane West''') <ref>{{cite book |last=Wortis Leider|first=Emily |title=Becoming Mae West|url=https://archive.org/details/becomingmaewest0000leid|publisher=Da Capo Press |date=2000 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/becomingmaewest0000leid/page/20 20]|isbn=0-306-80951-6}}</ref><ref name="Watts 2003 10">{{cite book|last=Watts|first=Jill |title=Mae West: An Icon in Black and White|url=https://archive.org/details/maewesticonblack00watt_502|publisher=Oxford University Press US|date=2003|pages=[https://archive.org/details/maewesticonblack00watt_502/page/n20 10]|isbn=0-195-16112-2}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=West|first=Mae|title=Goodness Had Nothing to Do With it|url=https://archive.org/details/goodnesshadnothi00west|publisher=Prentice-Hall|date=1959|pages=[https://archive.org/details/goodnesshadnothi00west/page/n20 1]}}</ref> ，是約翰·派翠克·蕙絲 (John Patrick West) 與瑪蒂妲·蒂莉·黛客 (Matilda "Tillie" Doelger/Delker) 兩人的女兒。<ref>{{cite book|last=Wortis Leider|first=Emily |title=Becoming Mae West|url=https://archive.org/details/becomingmaewest0000leid|publisher=Da Capo Press|date=2000|pages=[https://archive.org/details/becomingmaewest0000leid/page/23 23]|isbn=0-306-80951-6}}</ref>

